ActAn Act to amend the Controlled Drugs and Substances Act and to make related amendments to other Acts
SubjectOrder Fixing the Day on which this Order is made as the Day on which Certain Provisions of the Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing the day on which this Order is made as the day on which subsection 1(6), section 2, subsections 3(2) and 7(1) and (5), sections 8 and 10 to 24, subsection 26(8), sections 29, 54, 58 and 59, subsection 60(1) and sections 61, 64 to 68 and 70 to 72 of the ACT TO AMEND THE CONTROLLED DRUGS AND SUBSTANCES ACT AND TO MAKE RELATED AMENDMENTS TO OTHER ACTS, chapter 7 of the Statutes of Canada, 2017, COME INTO FORCE.
RegistrationRegistration: SI/ 2018-0046 Publication Date: 2018-07-11
